<section id="readingText">
	<h1>Writing Task 1</h1>
	<p>You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</p>
 	<p><b>You have just finished reading a book you think your friend would enjoy.</b></p>
	<p><b>Write a letter to your friend telling them about the book. Explain why you enjoyed it and recommend that they read it.</b></p>
	<p>You should write at least 150 words.</p>
	<p>You do&#xA0;<b>NOT</b>&#xA0;need to write your own address.</p>
	<p>Begin your letter as follows:</p>
	<p>Dear ...,</p>
</section>

<section id="body">
<ol id="splitquestionList">
	<li>Who do you have to write to?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t1">a stranger</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t2">an acquaintance</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t3">a colleague</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t4">a relative</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t5">a friend</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>What style of letter should you write?
	  <list class="answerList">
