		  <li><a id="t7">informal</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>What do you have to do in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t8">describe something</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t9">offer advice</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t10">give reasons</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t11">make a recommendation</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t12">express preferences</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	

	<li>How many points do you have to cover in this letter?
	  <list class="answerList">
		  <li><a id="t13">one</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t14">two</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t15">three</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t16">four</a></li>
		  <li><a id="t17">five</a></li>
	  </list></li>
	  <p class="linespace"></p>	

	<li>Which of the following would it be appropriate to write about in this letter?
